Background

		Ms. Stephanie W. Bergeron serves as the Chief Executive Officer and President at Bluepoint Partners LLC. Ms. Bergeron serves as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Walsh College, a leading premier non-profit institution that offers a broad range of innovative business and technology degrees and programs at three campuses and online. Ms. Bergeron served as Principal Accounting Officer of Goodyear Tire & Rubber Co. and served as its executive officer - worldwide ... corporate financial operations since February 5, 2002. She joined Goodyear Tire & Rubber Co. on December 29, 1998 and served as its Vice President and Treasurer from December 1998 to December 2003. Ms. Bergeron served as Senior Vice President of Corporate Financial Operations and Treasurer of Goodyear Tire and Rubber Company from February 5, 2002 to August 5, 2002. Prior thereto, she served as Vice President and Treasurer of Goodyear Tire and Rubber Company from December 1998 to December 2001. Prior thereto, she served as Vice President and Assistant Treasurer of Daimler Chrysler Corporation from November 1998 to December 1998. Ms. Bergeron served as Assistant Treasurer of Chrysler Corp. from November 1994 to November 1998. She served as Vice President and Assistant Treasurer Old Carco LLC. She serves as Vice Chair of Board of Trustees at Henry Ford Health System, Inc. Ms. Bergeron has been an Independent  Director at Sun Communities Inc. since May 22, 2007. She served as a Director of Superior Essex Inc. She served as a Director of Reynolds & Reynolds Co. since 2002. Ms. Bergeron received her bachelor's degree from the University of Michigan. She has master of business administration from University of Detroit.Read Full Background




