Insider Activity


Individual




Stephanie W. Bergeron



Ms. Stephanie W. Bergeron, CPA, is Independent Director at Sun Communities, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer at Walsh College, and President & Chief Executive Officer at Bluepoint Partners LLC. She is on the Board of Directors at Sun Communities, Inc. and Henry Ford Health System, Inc.
Ms. Bergeron was previously employed as Senior VP-Corporate Financial Operations by Goodyear Tire & Rubber Co., Vice President & Assistant Treasurer by DaimlerChrysler Corp., and a Director of Research by Office Remedies, Inc. She also served on the board at Superior Essex, Inc. and The Reynolds & Reynolds Co.



